<section class="trust">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="trust-content">
			<div class="trust-stats">
				<div class="stat-item">
					<div class="stat-number">25,000</div>
					<div class="stat-label">回以上の施術実績</div>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<div class="stat-number">90%</div>
					<div class="stat-label">初回で変化を実感</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="trust-text">
				<h2 class="trust-title">なぜ、他院では改善しないのか？</h2>
				<div class="trust-description">
					<p>
						多くの整体院や整骨院では、痛みのある部分だけにアプローチしています。しかし、それでは根本的な改善には至りません。
					</p>
					<p>
						痛みの<strong>本当の原因</strong>は、痛みを感じている場所とは別のところにあることがほとんどです。
					</p>
					<p>
						当院では、身体全体のバランスを見て、<strong>痛みの根本原因</strong>から改善していきます。だからこそ、他院で改善しなかった方々が、当院で結果を出されているのです。
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="trust-approach">
					<h3 class="approach-title">当院の3つのアプローチ</h3>
					<ul class="approach-list">
						<li>
							<span class="approach-number">1</span>
							<div class="approach-content">
								<strong>徹底したカウンセリング</strong>
								<p>症状の原因を根本から追求します</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="approach-number">2</span>
							<div class="approach-content">
								<strong>全身のバランス調整</strong>
								<p>痛みの部分だけでなく全身を整えます</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="approach-number">3</span>
							<div class="approach-content">
								<strong>セルフケア指導</strong>
								<p>再発防止のためのケア方法をお伝えします</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.trust {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--color-bg);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.trust::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 20%;
		right: -10%;
		width: 40%;
		height: 60%;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle at center,
			var(--color-secondary-light) 0%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		opacity: 0.06;
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 40px;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.trust-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.trust-stats {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		position: sticky;
		top: 120px;
	}

	.stat-item {
		background: linear-gradient(
			135deg,
			var(--color-primary) 0%,
			var(--color-accent) 100%
		);
		color: white;
		padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 32px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(212, 129, 111, 0.3);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.3s;
	}

	.stat-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -50%;
		right: -50%;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle at center,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0%,
			transparent 70%
		);
	}

	.stat-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.trust-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.trust-description {
		color: var(--color-text);
		line-height: 1.9;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.trust-description p {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.trust-description strong {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
	}

	.trust-approach {
		background: linear-gradient(
			135deg,
			var(--color-cream-light) 0%,
			white 100%
		);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 32px;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(212, 129, 111, 0.12);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.approach-title {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.approach-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 60px;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			var(--color-primary) 0%,
			var(--color-accent) 100%
		);
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	.approach-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.approach-list li {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: white;
		border-radius: 20px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.approach-list li:hover {
		transform: translateX(8px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(212, 129, 111, 0.15);
		border-color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.approach-number {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			135deg,
			var(--color-primary) 0%,
			var(--color-accent) 100%
		);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(212, 129, 111, 0.3);
	}

	.approach-content {
		flex: 1;
		padding-top: 0.25rem;
	}

	.approach-content strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.approach-content p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-light);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 30px;
		}

		.trust-content {
			gap: 3rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.trust {
			padding: 3rem 0;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 20px;
		}

		.trust-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}

		.trust-stats {
			flex-direction: row;
			position: static;
		}

		.stat-item {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.stat-label {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}

		.trust-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.trust-approach {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.approach-title {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.approach-list {
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.approach-list li {
			padding: 1.25rem;
		}

		.approach-number {
			width: 45px;
			height: 45px;
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.trust {
			padding: 2.5rem 0;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 16px;
		}

		.trust-content {
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.trust-stats {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.stat-item {
			padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.stat-label {
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			line-height: 1.4;
		}

		.trust-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
			line-height: 1.4;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.trust-description {
			font-size: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.trust-approach {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.approach-title {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.approach-list {
			gap: 1.25rem;
		}

		.approach-list li {
			padding: 1rem;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.approach-list li:hover {
			transform: translateX(4px);
		}

		.approach-number {
			width: 40px;
			height: 40px;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}

		.approach-content strong {
			font-size: 1.05rem;
		}

		.approach-content p {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 375px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 12px;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.stat-label {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
		}

		.trust-title {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.trust-description {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}

		.approach-title {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}

		.approach-content strong {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.approach-content p {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}
</style>
